-- BP Shares Increase After Installing New Cap on Leaking Gulf of Mexico Well
-- Stephen Cunningham
-- 2010-07-13T07:02:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/bp-shares-increase-after-installing-new-cap-on-leaking-gulf-of-mexico-well.html

          
          
             BP Plc rose 2.8 percent in London
trading after the company said it has installed a new cap on its
leaking Gulf of Mexico oil well and will start testing today
whether this will stop the gusher.  
          
          


  


        